Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.87,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,君を分かりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:43.16,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,僕と君は別々だから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.77,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,当たり前のもっと前から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.72,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,話をしようか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.88,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,伝達された花の名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.58,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,知らなくとも綺麗と言えること
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.02,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,頬に触れた暖かさを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.55,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,優しさだと呼び合えること
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:07.25,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,君は僕の、僕は君の、そばにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.18,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,君を分かりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.46,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,そのための涙さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:22.14,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,情けない僕だけど迎えに行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.49,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,言いたいのはただ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.84,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,悲しみも大嫌いも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:34.74,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,さよならも君がいるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.02,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.90,OP_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.87,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,想要了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:43.16,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我們終究有別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.77,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,所以在彼此交錯前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.72,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,互相傾訴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.88,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,君傳頌之花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:56.58,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,不曉其名也能欣賞它的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.02,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,觸碰你臉頰時的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.55,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,一定就是所謂的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:07.25,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,你與我 我與你 相互依偎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:12.18,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,想要了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.46,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,即使淚如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:22.14,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,軟弱的我仍義無反顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.49,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我想說的僅是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.84,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我能夠跨越悲傷 厭惡與離別
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:34.74,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,皆只因有你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:38.02,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.90,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,矢志不渝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:38.86,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}空の彼方約束を果たせるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:46.49,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}私はあなたと共に在りたいと願う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:48.60,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:53.30,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正しいとかそうじゃないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.65,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}自分次第だよって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:23:03.52,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}頭で分かってるつもり心は連れない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:10.43,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時として言葉は心を現わすには不十分だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:12.49,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}しょうがないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:15.95,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}弱い自分裏返す強い自分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:21.50,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}あなたに相応しい私でいられるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:25.98,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.98,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}失くせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:32.47,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}諦められないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.34,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Keeping promises
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.97,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}誓うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.31,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}辿る空で待っていると
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:40.51,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:41.73,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:44.67,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}自分の心に届いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:45.67,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:48.76,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}残された二日を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:49.91,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.91,0:23:52.64,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}決意は揺るがない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:53.77,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:56.49,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}もう一人の自分にグッバイ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:58.22,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:38.86,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}去實現於天空彼方的約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:46.49,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈願與你並肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:48.60,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:53.30,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正確與否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.65,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:23:03.52,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:10.43,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而詞不達意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.43,0:23:12.49,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:15.95,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}讓弱小的我變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:21.50,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是為與你相稱
Comment: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:25.98,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I ain’t fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.98,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:32.47,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如無法放棄
Comment: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.34,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Keeping promises
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.97,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}既然立下誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.31,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我將在彼方守候
Comment: 0,0:23:39.31,0:23:40.51,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}I meant for you
Comment: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:41.73,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:44.67,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}直達內心
Comment: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:45.67,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Mind’s eye flickers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.67,0:23:48.76,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}擁抱僅剩的兩日
Comment: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:49.91,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}We are Drifters
